rows.label: qst002902_msg0001
rows.name:
Please give the Linka
Honey to Tsubutsubu, mo.

rows.label: qst002902_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't need anything else, mo.
Give it to Shibushibu, mo.

rows.label: qst002902_msg0003
rows.name: I still want more Linka Honey, mo.

rows.label: qst002902_msg0004
rows.name:
With this much, I can take
a Linka Honey bath, mo!

rows.label: qst002902_msg0005
rows.name:
I was tricked into coming
to this remote place, but
it was worth it, mo.
